➜「益阳千玺」「全村耻辱」...为啥当代年轻人爱把「沙雕」写在衣服上？
http://www.sohu.com/a/411163254_425113	8772
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200803/f7c1aea7ce4545ccab1caf4569ff86ca.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200803/5a06f815de6e4dd7987450569367009b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">曾几何时，<strong>穿衣打扮</strong>多讲究得体美观</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但现如今，这早已变成</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一种<strong>张扬个性</strong>的表达方式</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在这个彰显个性化的时代</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为了展现自己特立独行的主张</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">越来越多的年轻人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把衣服穿成了行走的个性签名和表情包</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200803/375e965cae974b57bb80181b7b3290d5.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">今天文字君就来带大家欣赏一下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当代年轻人是如何</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>用一件衣服的时间</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>把自己打扮为gai上最受瞩目的仔</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200803/f033cbcb54ef432ca676d905bc2e20b7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在这个啥都讲求快准狠的年代</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一份个性鲜明的<strong>自我介绍</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就好比一项大写加粗的技能Buff</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">能够让你在各种场合下发光发亮</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">成为人群中最耀眼的存在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但当疫情突如其来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">并且全员戴上口罩以后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文字君发现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在自我介绍这件大事上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再好的口才也发挥不了什么作用</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">茫茫人海中，如何让对方</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一眼看到并记住自己？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最好的方法就是<strong>写在衣服</strong>上！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200803/a47a5d35b96b472588eb8e578a8e45f8.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">像这样，把个人气质提炼出来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再配以亲近的“小X”称谓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直接印在衣服上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就最醒目不过了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200803/ff2dccf87b08483592b148fe3d6b9ff9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">试想一下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当路上迎面走来一个“全村的希望”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那衣服上抖动的几个大字</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是否像极了一张放大加粗的名片？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200803/c23dccc890f348079944bac20ccd44eb.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">很多人在自我介绍之前</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都会精挑细选、字斟句酌、思前想后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">力求展现出最优秀的自己</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然而再多华丽的词藻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都比不上一眼就能达到“本地吴彦祖”的穿衣效果</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200803/ecf45c3716504390af821f98b0289f2c.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没错，当代年轻人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">头发可以乱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但衣服一定要帅要吸睛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如若不好意思在人前太过自夸</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">又想小小地炫耀一把的话</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就可以借由衣服的口吻来夸赞自己</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200803/d55932b598fd4b3988abfeac540fe630.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就算把“全国境内未醉过”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这种豪言壮语穿在身上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">别人也不会觉得你在装逼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">即便“国家一级熬夜运动员</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">退堂鼓表演艺术家</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">放鸽活动策划人”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这种略显羞涩的身份</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也会让人肃然起敬</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200803/2e6f739032a049068256b5e58579a0a3.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200803/0e208f206b384643be5ae3387c8e7179.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有时候，穿一件表达情绪的衣服出门</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其效果就相当于</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">发了一条一天可见的朋友圈</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">对于当代年轻人而言</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最想借衣服发“圈”的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当然要数<strong>上班</strong>那些事儿了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">作为一名合格的社畜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">首要的职场生存技能就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要坦然面对无穷无尽的加班</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只要老板一声令下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就得从约会聚餐的路上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">火速赶赴公司</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">开启工作模式</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">槽多无口的加班狗们只能通过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">胸口印大字的方式来调侃自己：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">谁让我是<strong>社会主义加班人</strong>呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我加班我光荣！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200803/fe5092b1d99147a9bbe54df59040a168.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果有一件衣服能精准描述出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">社畜日常内心独白的话</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那么它一定写着<strong>“这个需求做不了”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200803/498921d3f7bc43a09d8f32388d308c3f.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就算引来老板和客户的质疑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你也可以辩解说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这只是衣服的设计艺术</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">同样，在面对同事甩锅的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">社畜们最想借由衣服抒发的话</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是<strong>“这锅你自己背去吧”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200803/e11d262a88fb43ea96c6ea04a3635477.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">说到底，上班族的烦恼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有一半都是没钱造成的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">工作忙起来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就算很累很想休息</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只要一想到花呗没还清</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就吓得要换件衣服来鞭策自己</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>没钱不能任性</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200803/162091fecdef441b9eee790aa543e70d.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">本以为通过任劳任怨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就能够换来相对高的报酬</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">万万没想到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">钱包的进账速度</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">远远比不过掏空的速度</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有时候必须把“四大皆空”印在衣服上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才能杜绝商家的招揽套路</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">否则一踏出公司大门</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就会被买买买口号惊扰到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200803/912a5c32050544dfafd3e326c7c29def.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200803/ab9d28375a2a4e08a7ab99cf4d34ada4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">现在的年轻人最擅长的就是<strong>自黑</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自黑的舞台从来不拘泥于形式</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一件衣服往往也有出其不意的效果</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在旁观自黑的道路上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你总会不经意间被那么几件</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">骚上天的衣服笑到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有些单身狗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">向来敢于把自黑自嘲的话语</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">打在公屏上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟颜值拼不过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就要拼坦诚幽默</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200803/92f64ad98da84fcfbecace20d0776bb2.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">与其让周围人来吐槽自己</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还不如自己下手更知道分寸</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">正所谓：黑到极致自然红</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>自黑到一定境界</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>就能收获关于真性情人设的赞美</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200803/8116699f9017403395fb418b623ef3e6.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但偏偏有些男生反其道而行之</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">别人自黑只是谦虚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他自黑是真的自黑 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还没找女朋友</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就把话堵死在衣服上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">分分钟想气死全世界女生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200803/a0a54daab491433b97ca4803113afe35.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过据文字君观察</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一般自称是“渣男”“海王”的男生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都只是嫌麻烦、想省事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而有些戏精的自黑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就纯粹是为了搞笑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大家好，本人资产35亿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不好意思，都是假的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">开篇引人入胜，结局出人意外</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">简直是一篇山曲十八弯的小作文</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200803/ce777ae0324d471daeaf1fb8d045de1c.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">除了自嘲爱发白日梦以外</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">年轻人也常吐槽自己是婚恋市场黑洞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在婚恋市场中，千怕万怕</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最怕丈母娘的挑剔</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这件T恤更像是对彩礼的吐槽</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200803/b8089aaa8863433f8ca40e91d37eb287.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200803/ea3f190ed0b947fbaf505b3f4db2195d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文化衫一直以来都是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">作为<strong>团队宣传</strong>手段出现的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如企业、班级等集体</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都特别喜欢用统一文字图案的T恤</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来彰显团队的凝聚力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自从表情包文化流行开来以后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">年轻人突发奇想</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在衣服上印刷表情包和个性签名</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把DIY文化衫真正变成了独一无二的个性化穿着</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200803/490912e667674195858e17db3d8ae4ee.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">表情包和个性签名都是情绪的表达</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它包含着一种略带苦涩的幽默</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和几分自黑的勇气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">年轻人在外漂泊，拼命工作加班</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还要面对各种压力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">被生活逼得喘不过来气时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在衣服上打打嘴炮</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这是年轻人对这个世界能做的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最幽默的唯一反抗a</p>
